2006-01-11  Brian Cameron  <brian.cameron@sun.com>

	* daemon/verify-crypt.c, daemon/verify-pam.c, daemon/verify-shadow.c,
	  docs/C/gdm.xml, gui/greeter/greeter_parser.c:  Change the
