Fri Aug 31 18:21:46 2001  George Lebl <jirka@5z.com>

	* daemon/xdmcp.c: run the Willing script at most once every 3
	  seconds.  That way we can prevent some DOS attacks.

	* docs/C/gdm.sgml: update

