	life in thawed mode.

1998-11-22  Martin Kasper Petersen  <mkp@mkp.net>

	* src/gdmgreeter.c (gdm_greeter_browser_select): Reverted to the
 	old event types (GDK_BUTTON_PRESS) for gnome-icon-list.

