 	server.

	* src/gdm.c (gdm_config_parse): Added intelligent AuthDir
 	searching and gdmLogDir. gdmLogFile deprecated.

	* src/gdmslave.c (gdm_slave_init): Moved stdout, stderr logging
 	here. Logs are now per-display.

